# Local-only endpoints used by the install pattern, never reachable from CI.
http://127\.0\.0\.1:3001/.*
http://localhost:3001/.*

# Pre-release links that resolve once v1.0.0 tag is published.
https://github\.com/Vahlame/obsidian-memory-kit/releases/tag/v.*
https://github\.com/Vahlame/obsidian-memory-kit/compare/.*

# Self-repo ADR deep-links from the npm README (absolute URLs are required there —
# npmjs.com can't resolve relative paths). They 404 only until this PR merges to
# main, then resolve permanently — same case as the pre-release links above.
https://github\.com/Vahlame/obsidian-memory-kit/blob/main/docs/adr/.*

